{"tid":2094853,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：不評論日媒報導「支那武警駐港」一說","createTime":"2020-07-05T04:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:04:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"743f1f48112f2c89a8f766b322eb595ee23b801d","tid":2094853,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"政府不評論報道指北京將派遣武警駐港<br />\n05.07.2020 12:14<br />\n<br />\n日本共同社引述消息說，北京為貫徹港區國安法，將派遣200至300名武警以觀察員身份駐港。港府回應指，不評論揣測性報道，又指履行港區國安法工作的人員都會遵守香港法律。<br />\n<br />\n港區國安法明確規定分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、恐怖活動、勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全等4類罪行和相應處罰。而在內地，武警其中一項主要職責是擔負反恐任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329631&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1329631%26csid%3D261_341&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=fa6134a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329631&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8304d02bb6198cdc9b12e45f6efd7749539e833b","tid":2094853,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"即係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bc28b594362114c18a17d5b7b1c6f07b061eb4","tid":2094853,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8304d02bb6198cdc9b12e45f6efd7749539e833b","tid":2094853,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"即係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a07cf7ba3a985f6746e15af0785eaa274a64454","tid":2094853,"uid":155095,"like":3,"di